Invocation Name: confidently flawed
des:
Start your day with Confidently Flawed Inspires, a list of quotes to Confidently begin, boost, and/or end your day. Just say "Alexa, open Confidently Flawed" to get your first quote. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
